snippet.title: Favignano Live
snippet.description:
This is a channel that hosts all of my Twitch livestream archives.
I stream live on twitch Tuesday - Friday (Sometimes weekends)
twitch.tv/jfavignano

*PC* Sponsored by Jetline Systems
NZXT S340 Elite Mid-Tower (Black)
Gigabyte Aorus Z370 Gaming 7, LGA 1151
Intel 8th Gen Core i7 8700K (5.0GHz Overclock) Six Core
32GB (2x16GB) Corsair DDR4 SDRAM 3000MHz
EVGA GeForce RTX 2080 Super
1TB Samsung 960 EVO Solid State Drive

*AUDIO*
Electro-Voice RE-20 Microphone
CL-1 Cloudlifter
GOXLR Mixer
Sony MDR-7506 Headphones

This channel is a part of the Full Screen network
